<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dalliance" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dalliance,</orth> 1) trifling, toying, wanton play: <cit><quote>do not give d. too much the rein,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.1.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 1, 51</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you use this d. to excuse your breach of promise,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 48</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 48</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 2.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 2.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.1.23" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 1, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.3.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 3, 50</bibl>.<lb />2) tarrying: <cit><quote>keep not back your powers in d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.2.5" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 2, 5</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>